content:
Monitor Net Zero Cloud changes with Field History Tracking. 
This feature is available for customers with New Zero Cloud enabled.
From Setup, enter Field History Tracking, select it, click View on an object, enable tracking, and then select the fields to track.
Where: This change applies to Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs), Lightning Experience, and various editions of the Salesforce app.
title: Summer '24 Release Notes for Salesforce
